{"tid":2251543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視曝光驅離外國戰機影片 全片沒外機蹤影 網友：隱形戰機？","createTime":"2020-10-21T01:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T04:00:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"71cba4620d9aeb492c32f3843f1b6df2c3d37889","tid":2251543,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:11:43.000Z","msg":"中國官媒「央視」，19號發布「驅離外機」影片，引發中國網友火大痛罵，原來片中完全沒見到其他國家軍機，遭中國網友酸，根本是隱形戰機吧；恰巧美軍也有動作，19號派出電偵機到中國東南沿海進行偵察，距離中國領海基線只有短短50海里；不過，中國空軍20號上午，又再度出動，派出三型機潛入我西南空域，國防部全程監控。<br />\n<br />\n外機來犯，中國飛行員廣播驅離，秀軍事肌肉，事後飛行員還現身說法，雙方在空中如何鬥法。中國軍機飛行員羅威說，「已經看清楚它的機徽機號，對方飛機立即向我們壓坡度，當對方發現通過盤旋壓坡度方式，無法擺脫我的時候，他們就遠離我方的海岸線。」<br />\n<br />\n明明近到看得清機徽、機號；但說來奇怪，這段驅離外機的影片，卻不見任何外機蹤影，有中國網友就質疑，哪有外機？還有人說沒看到就對了嘛，人家是隱形飛機。中國有沒有驅離外機，成了羅生門，但屢屢擾台都有紀錄，20號又入侵我西南空域，根據國防部發布訊息指出，中國解放軍派遣一架空警500預警機、一架運9通信對抗機、一架運8三型機，進入我西南空域活動，國軍立刻派遣空中巡邏兵力應對，並以防空飛彈追監；據了解，空軍10月份至少53次廣播驅離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2020A20P16M1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftvnews.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2020A20P16M1&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=8abdf42d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2020A20P16M1</a>"},{"pid":"53471e533e2d6d68c74e73af8291d8f79bdce76c","tid":2251543,"uid":371815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"柒頭解放狗諗住扮做嘢出嚟威，點知比人發現假大空，真羞家"},{"pid":"94afecf5380e0d1c42b461e10da057f8b9fe8d24","tid":2251543,"uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:14:02.000Z","msg":"光學隱形"},{"pid":"4637be503385d3a02e935c8a299ff9e825a67b75","tid":2251543,"uid":285868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:20:17.000Z","msg":"原來美軍已經做到光學隱形<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21f7797782f9ab963630ebc90079b57f009084f","tid":2251543,"uid":76867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:20:39.000Z","msg":"佢地見到仲唔拿拿臨調頭走咩"},{"pid":"2e17be5e20dfef1a8d54fee83bbad191bca3d2dc","tid":2251543,"uid":57291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4637be503385d3a02e935c8a299ff9e825a67b75","tid":2251543,"uid":285868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:20:17.000Z","msg":"原來美軍已經做到光學隱形<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:27:38.000Z","msg":"解放軍已經做到肉眼識破光學迷彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdeebd123f767c5f7b43f80440dbff9f5184f7f","tid":2251543,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"繼國王的新衣後，又一糸列國王的戰機，好快有國王的大國，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b51cb7cf7138d48db6f26ffba5434f8f2ffd47","tid":2251543,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"是咪好似佢d實彈演習咁"},{"pid":"b348722b524e65a7e5bd56226e2873d99e8767e1","tid":2251543,"uid":261937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"隱形戰機只可騙過六感中其中一感，解放軍還有其餘五感去捕捉敵機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c34c076c4edcfe07d77a7d731b0fc5dd81c7287","tid":2251543,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"幻想緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b253654bf0c65e3957b44b5d731e71faa7e566","tid":2251543,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b348722b524e65a7e5bd56226e2873d99e8767e1","tid":2251543,"uid":261937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"隱形戰機只可騙過六感中其中一感，解放軍還有其餘五感去捕捉敵機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse